"title": "4817: drought, spiritual",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4817",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Scripture indicates that believers, both as individuals and communities, may go through periods in which they fail to experience the refreshing and life-giving presence of God. One cause of such spiritual thirst is unbelief. Scripture also indicates ways in which this thirst may be relieved.</p>\n<h2>Spiritual drought in unbelievers</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps68:6\">PSA 68:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa29:7-Isa29:8\">ISA 29:7–29:8</a></p>\n<h3>The remedy for spiritual drought is to be found in Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:37-John7:39\">JHN 7:37–7:39</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa45:8\">ISA 45:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:1\">ISA 55:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:13-John4:14\">JHN 4:13–4:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:5-Titus3:7\">TIT 3:5–3:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:17\">REV 22:17</a></p>\n<h2>The experience of spiritual drought in believers</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps63:1\">PSA 63:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps143:6\">PSA 143:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek19:10-Ezek19:14\">EZK 19:10–19:14</a></p>\n<h2>The cause of spiritual drought in believers</h2>\n<h3>Unconfessed sin</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps32:3-Ps32:4\">PSA 32:3–32:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps66:18\">PSA 66:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:28-Isa1:30\">ISA 1:28–1:30</a></p>\n<h3>Spiritual depression</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps42:1-Ps42:2\">PSA 42:1–42:2</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Self-reliance</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer2:13\">JER 2:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:5-Jer17:6\">JER 17:5–17:6</a></p>\n<h3>God's judgment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos8:11\">AMO 8:11</a></strong></p>\n<h2>The remedy for spiritual drought in the lives of believers</h2>\n<h3>Through confession</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:8-1John1:9\">1JN 1:8–1:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps32:5\">PSA 32:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps51:12\">PSA 51:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:19-1John3:22\">1JN 3:19–3:22</a></p>\n<h3>Through Scripture</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps1:2-Ps1:3\">PSA 1:2–1:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:1-Deut32:2\">DEU 32:1–32:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:10-Isa55:11\">ISA 55:10–55:11</a></p>\n<h3>Through Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:35\">JHN 6:35</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:37-John7:39\">JHN 7:37–7:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:7-Jas5:8\">JAS 5:7–5:8</a></p>\n<h3>Through the Holy Spirit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:3\">ISA 44:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa32:13-Isa32:15\">ISA 32:13–32:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:13\">ROM 15:13</a></p>\n<h3>Finally in heaven</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev7:16-Rev7:17\">REV 7:16–7:17</a></strong></p>",
